              "free_text": [
                " The neutron fluence was determi-",
                "ned with a fission chamber of U-238. During the expe-",
                "riment solid angles subtended for the neutron source",
                "by the targets of Ni-58, Fe-54 and the U-238 sample,",
                "about 8 degrees, remained unchanged. The recommended",
                "data of ENDF/B-6 for U-238(n,f) were used for deriving",
                "the total cross section."
              ]
